<h2><b>Overview of 10 Free AI Trading Bots </b></h2>
<h3><b>1. BulkQuant – AI Trading Bot for Crypto and Stock Automation </b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-200756 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/image7-1.jpg" alt="1. BulkQuant – AI Trading Bot for Crypto and Stock Automation " width="1883" height="1020" /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BulkQuant is a platform that offers managed automated trading strategies for crypto and stock markets. It includes features such as real-time analytics and simplified setup, which may appeal to beginners. </span></p>
<ul>
